      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>
      My students are very diverse and have different language problems. After five years of teaching, having passed the DaF certificate for teachers and having done a lot of additional teacher trainings, I decided to try out my first didactic game, or tool, that would make German language learning <strong>instructive</strong>, <strong>interactive</strong>, <strong>interesting</strong> and <strong>fun</strong>. With the help of my product, you will be able to master the German language and improve your existing skills, as you can work with one cube or add any number of cubes to increase the difficulty of the task ahead of you.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you have any feedback, suggestion, or simply want to chat, feel free to send me an email at
      <a target="_blank" href="mailto:maja@majaslernspass.si" title="Maja">maja@majaslernspass.si</a>.
    </p>

